snippet.title: Framing Dawes, Part One: Thyme to Leave (Official Demo Trailer)
snippet.description:
Bay Dawes is not your typical teenager. She has a dead pet rabbit called Dink, and a curious case of phobophilia (love of fear). However, after receiving an email from an unknown sender accusing her of murder, Dawes' life is turned upside down... Literally.

Demo coming soon to:
https://jinxitgames.itch.io/framing-dawes-demo
And then to Steam - more details to follow...

Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Caroline_JinxIt
Follow on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/FramingDawes/
Follow on Instagram: https://instagram.com/jinx_it_games

Thanks for watching!
